      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478299,
      "updated": 1524478299
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb158aff09e000045fb31",
      "text": " [勾配降下法の最適化アルゴリズム https://www.slideshare.net/nishio/ss-66840545]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478297,
      "updated": 1524478316
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb1bbaff09e000045fb34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478396,
      "updated": 1524478396
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb166aff09e000045fb33",
      "text": "\t高次元の関数に関して、勾配が0である点(停留点)のほとんどは鞍点である。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478310,
      "updated": 1524478415
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb1cfaff09e000045fb36",
      "text": " \t10次元の場合で99.8%",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478415,
      "updated": 1524478421
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb2b9aff09e000045fb38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478650,
      "updated": 1524478650
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb1d4aff09e000045fb37",
      "text": " [効用関数]の最大化という観点でとらえるならこういうストーリーになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478421,
      "updated": 1524478666
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb2c9aff09e000045fb39",
      "text": " \t今の製品からあまり離れない製品の中から、もっとも効用関数が大きくなる物を選ぶ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478666,
      "updated": 1524478747
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb31baff09e000045fb3a",
      "text": "  \t＝今の製品で表現される点の勾配に基づいて、最も勾配が大きくなる方向へ更新する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478747,
      "updated": 1524478764
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb32caff09e000045fb3b",
      "text": "  それを繰り返していると鞍点に到達する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478764,
      "updated": 1524498902
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb338aff09e000045fb3c",
      "text": "  鞍点に来るまでに進んできた方向に進んでも効用は減少する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478777,
      "updated": 1524478799
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb34faff09e000045fb3d",
      "text": "  まったく違う方向に進む必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478799,
      "updated": 1524478805
    },
    {
      "id": "5addb1c1aff09e000045fb35",
      "text": "\t\t#要実験",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1524478401,
      "updated": 1524478897
    },
